<activity xml:id="act-conozcamos-menosLoMismoMas-imagenes" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Conozcamos “Menos, lo mismo, más: Imágenes”</title>

<statement>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-171813">
    <shortdescription>Centro menos, lo mismo, más.</shortdescription>
  </image>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p>Students place images of 1, 2, 3, and 4 on the left.</p>
  <p>Students place images of 5 in the middle.</p>
  <p>Students place images of 6, 7, 8, 9, and 10 on the right.</p>
</solution>


